@startuml fig-tcp-header
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
left to right direction
title Antetul TCP (20-60 octeti)

card "Port Sursa\n16 biti" as sp #BBDEFB
card "Port Dest\n16 biti" as dp #BBDEFB
card "Numar Secventa\n32 biti" as seq #C8E6C9
card "Numar Confirmare\n32 biti" as ack #C8E6C9
card "Flag-uri\nSYN ACK FIN RST" as fl #FFF9C4
card "Fereastra\n16 biti" as win #FFE0B2
card "Checksum\n16 biti" as cs #FFCDD2

legend bottom
Secventa: pozitia octetului in flux
Confirmare: urmatorul octet asteptat
Fereastra: spatiu buffer receptor
Flag-uri: SYN=conectare, FIN=inchidere, RST=anulare
Comune: SYN, SYN-ACK, ACK, FIN-ACK
endlegend
@enduml
